text: Murder at 1600 is a 1997 American action thriller movie directed by Dwight H. Little and starring Wesley Snipes, Diane Lane, Daniel Benzali, Dennis Miller, Alan Alda, Ronny Cox, Diane Baker, Tate Donovan, Harris Yulin, Nicholas Pryor, Pamela Salem. It was distributed by Warner Bros. and was a box office disappointment. ==Other websites== * * * * * * Category:1997 action movies Category:1997 thriller movies Category:American action movies Category:American thriller movies Category:Warner Bros. movies Category:Movies directed by Dwight H. Little
